These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, monopoly, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, drama, satire
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person playing canasta is the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | bridge | monopoly | snooker | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | action     | drama   | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower, iris, dahlia
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, van, boat, tram
1. the person who growsdahlia is the person driving the van##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | iris | dahlia | balloon-flower | daffodil    |
| Transport   | boat    | van      | car | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, baseball, tennis, sailing
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indian, french, italian
1. the french is on the left of the italian##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the canadian##1
3. the indian is on the far right##1
4. the italian is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Sport         | biathlon | sailing | tennis   | baseball |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french | italian | indian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, train, bike, motorbike
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, board-games, reading
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | motorbike | train | airplane  | bike      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | reading   | board-games | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy, documentary, superhero
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, fishing, sudoku, card-games
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | documentary | spy | fantasy |
| Hobby    | reading       | card-games | sudoku | fishing     |

