.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, billiard, poker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia, zinnia, marigold
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Game   | poker | billiard | bridge | mah-jongg |
| Flower           | amaryllis      | zinnia | marigold | dahlia    |

