.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
House: tower, townhouse, cape-cod, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, collecting, reading
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
2. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| House   | cape-cod | townhouse | tower | futuristic  |
| Hobby           | collecting | skydiving | reading       | puzzles |

