.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, frog, fish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, soy-milk, milk
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person drinking milk is the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Pet         | frog | hedgehog      | mouse | fish |
| Beverage   | lemonade          | juice | soy-milk     | milk    |

