.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rugby, swimming, parkour
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, february, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Sport   | rugby    | swimming       | badminton | parkour   |
| Birthday     | may | february | march   | september |

