.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, rowing, basketball
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, gospel, rock
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Sport    | snowboarding | rowing  | climbing | basketball |
| Music-Genre   | rock | gospel | r&b          | d&b    |

