.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, ritmeester, montecristo, tiparillo
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, billiard, bridge
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Cigar      | montecristo | ritmeester  | old-henry | tiparillo |
| Game   | backgammon  | billiard | bridge           | whist   |

