.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, motorbike, boat, quad-bike
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, chaman, swisher, dannemann
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | train | quad-bike | boat  |
| Cigar           | dannemann | chaman      | swisher | tiparillo |

