3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | march | july  | august | may   |
| Sport        | golf | rugby | weightlifting    | parkour |

