.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros, pall-mall, bluemaster
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, horse, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar   | oliveros      | pall-mall | bluemaster | ritmeester |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | ferret    | horse  | pony |

