3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Sport      | water-polo   | sailing | surfing   | climbing      |
| Flower   | bellflower | tulip      | iris | aconite |

