.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, dutch, colombian, brazilian
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, billiard, monopoly
1. the colombian is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing billiard is the colombian##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | dutch | colombian | brazilian | french |
| Game   | monopoly     | billiard    | mah-jongg      | canasta   |

