.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, january, february
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, iced-tea, fanta
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | november | january | december | february   |
| Beverage     | iced-tea  | hot-chocolate    | 7up       | fanta |

 